View vw_allindiadatatriangulation
Query
 
CREATE VIEW ${fullName} AS  SELECT b.clientkey,
    b.companykey,
    'All India'::text AS "?column?",
    b.fiscalyearvariantkey,
    b.fiscalyear,
    f.fiscalyeardisplay,
    e.estimatetypename,
    sea.seasonname,
    u.useragencyshortdesc AS useragencyname,
    c.cropname AS crop,
    cat.cropcategoryname AS cropcategory,
    subcat.cropsubcategoryname AS cropsubcategory,
    b.account,
    b.value
   FROM (((((((( SELECT '1'::text AS clientkey,
            'MOA'::text AS companykey,
            'C2'::text AS fiscalyearvariantkey,
            a.fiscalyear,
            a.estimationtypekey,
            a.seasonkey,
            '001'::text AS "?column?",
            3 AS "?column?",
            5 AS useragencykey,
            a.cropkey,
            a.account,
            a.value,
            ''::text AS "?column?"
           FROM ( SELECT datatriangulation.fiscalyear,
                    datatriangulation.estimationtypekey,
                    datatriangulation.seasonkey,
                    datatriangulation.cropkey,
                    datatriangulation.account,
                    sum((datatriangulation.value * (datatriangulation.scalling)::numeric)) AS value
                   FROM upag.datatriangulation
                  WHERE (datatriangulation.useragencykey = 5)
                  GROUP BY datatriangulation.fiscalyear, datatriangulation.estimationtypekey, datatriangulation.seasonkey, datatriangulation.cropkey, datatriangulation.account) a) b(clientkey, companykey, fiscalyearvariantkey, fiscalyear, estimationtypekey, seasonkey, "?column?", "?column?_1", useragencykey, cropkey, account, value, "?column?_2")
     JOIN upag.fiscalyeartext f ON (((b.clientkey = (f.clientkey)::text) AND (b.companykey = (f.companykey)::text) AND (f.fiscalyearkey = b.fiscalyear) AND ((f.fiscalyearvariantkey)::text = b.fiscalyearvariantkey))))
     JOIN upag.estimatetype e ON (((b.clientkey = (e.clientkey)::text) AND (b.companykey = (e.companykey)::text) AND (b.estimationtypekey = e.estimatetypekey))))
     JOIN upag.season sea ON (((b.clientkey = (sea.clientkey)::text) AND (b.companykey = (sea.companykey)::text) AND (sea.seasonkey = b.seasonkey))))
     JOIN upag.useragencytext u ON (((b.clientkey = (u.clientkey)::text) AND (b.companykey = (u.companykey)::text) AND (b.useragencykey = u.useragencykey))))
     JOIN upag.crop c ON (((b.clientkey = (c.clientkey)::text) AND (b.companykey = (c.companykey)::text) AND (b.cropkey = c.cropkey))))
     JOIN upag.cropcategory cat ON (((b.clientkey = (cat.clientkey)::text) AND (b.companykey = (cat.companykey)::text) AND (c.cropcategorykey = cat.cropcategorykey))))
     JOIN upag.cropsubcategory subcat ON (((b.clientkey = (subcat.clientkey)::text) AND (b.companykey = (subcat.companykey)::text) AND (c.cropsubcategorykey = subcat.cropsubcategorykey))))
IdxField NameData Type
  clientkey text
  companykey text
  ?column? text
  fiscalyearvariantkey text
  fiscalyear integer
  fiscalyeardisplay varchar(50)
  estimatetypename varchar(100)
  seasonname varchar(100)
  useragencyname varchar(50)
  crop varchar(100)
  cropcategory varchar(100)
  cropsubcategory varchar(100)
  account varchar(100)
  value numeric


View vw_croppricing
Query
 
CREATE VIEW ${fullName} AS  SELECT c.cropname AS crop,
    cat.cropcategoryname,
    subcat.cropsubcategoryname,
    "left"(u."Year", 4) AS fiscalyear,
    initcap(u.season_name) AS seasonname,
    u.minimum_support_price
   FROM (((upag."6004" u
     JOIN upag.crop c ON ((lower(TRIM(BOTH FROM c.cropname)) = lower(TRIM(BOTH FROM u.commodity_name)))))
     JOIN upag.cropcategory cat ON ((cat.cropcategorykey = c.cropcategorykey)))
     JOIN upag.cropsubcategory subcat ON ((subcat.cropsubcategorykey = c.cropsubcategorykey)))
IdxField NameData Type
  crop varchar(100)
  cropcategoryname varchar(100)
  cropsubcategoryname varchar(100)
  fiscalyear text
  seasonname text
  minimum_support_price integer


View vw_submissions
Query
 
CREATE VIEW ${fullName} AS  SELECT a.clientkey,
    a.companykey,
    a.statekey,
    a.isocode,
    a.statename,
    a.fiscalyearkey AS fiscalyear,
    a.estimatetypekey,
    a.status,
    f.requestprocessstatuskey,
        CASE
            WHEN (f.requestprocessstatuskey = 8) THEN 'Verification Pending'::character varying
            ELSE COALESCE(r.requestprocessstatusname, 'Not Submitted'::character varying)
        END AS requestprocessstatusname
   FROM ((( SELECT s.clientkey,
            s.companykey,
            s.statekey,
            s.isocode,
            s.statename,
            s.locationcoding,
            fe.fiscalyearkey,
            fe.fiscalyearvariantkey,
            fe.estimatetypekey,
            fe.status
           FROM (upag.state s
             CROSS JOIN upag.fiscalyearestimatetype fe)
          WHERE ((s.locationcoding)::text = 'LGD'::text)) a
     LEFT JOIN ( SELECT fileuploaddatatracking.clientkey,
            fileuploaddatatracking.companykey,
            fileuploaddatatracking.requestid,
            fileuploaddatatracking.useragencykey,
            fileuploaddatatracking.typeofdataingestion,
            fileuploaddatatracking.uploadedon,
            fileuploaddatatracking.uploadedby,
            fileuploaddatatracking.requeststatuskey,
            fileuploaddatatracking.requestprocessstatuskey,
            fileuploaddatatracking.year,
            fileuploaddatatracking.approvedby,
            fileuploaddatatracking.approvedon,
            fileuploaddatatracking.statekey,
            fileuploaddatatracking.estimationtypekey,
            fileuploaddatatracking.remarks
           FROM upag.fileuploaddatatracking
          WHERE ((fileuploaddatatracking.useragencykey = 4) AND (fileuploaddatatracking.requestprocessstatuskey = ANY (ARRAY[6, 7, 8])))) f ON (((f.statekey = a.statekey) AND (f.estimationtypekey = a.estimatetypekey))))
     LEFT JOIN upag.requestprocessstatus r ON ((r.requestprocessstatuskey = f.requestprocessstatuskey)))
IdxField NameData Type
  clientkey varchar(3)
  companykey varchar(4)
  statekey integer
  isocode varchar(10)
  statename varchar(100)
  fiscalyear integer
  estimatetypekey integer
  status varchar(40)
  requestprocessstatuskey integer
  requestprocessstatusname varchar
